## Description {#details}

<a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/arrayref">ArrayRef</a> is not really compatible with the YAMLTraits.

Everything should be immutable in an <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/arrayref">ArrayRef</a>, while the <a href="/docs/api/structs/llvm/yaml/sequencetraits">SequenceTraits</a> expect a mutable version for inputting, but we&#39;re only using the outputting capabilities here. This is a hack, but still nicer than having to manually call the YAMLIO internal methods. Keep this in this file so that it doesn&#39;t get misused from <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/support/yamltraits-h">YAMLTraits.h</a>.
